      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under steady-state operating conditions. COU involves same device class and similar flow regimes. The GW model linear superposition assumption is cited as broadly applicable to turbomachinery flows; no dedicated test of this assumption under CPB pulsatile conditions was conducted, but overall relevance assessed as adequate for MRL 2.",
